metaTags.metaTitle: Cloudflare Turnstile, a free CAPTCHA replacement
metaTags.metaDescription: Cloudflare Turnstile is a simple, free CAPTCHA replacement so web visitors have great, CAPTCHA-free experiences.

promotionalBanner.desktopText: Cloudflare's global network protects and accelerates everything on the Internet.

relatedBlades.title: Free CAPTCHA Alternative
relatedBlades.subtitle: Cloudflare Turnstile is a free tool to replace CAPTCHAs
relatedBlades.copy: Turnstile delivers frustration-free, CAPTCHA-free web experiences to website visitors - with just a simple snippet of free code. Moreover, Turnstile stops abuse and confirms visitors are real without the data privacy concerns or awful UX that CAPTCHAs thrust on users.
relatedBlades.leftLink: [Enterprise plans include Turnstile, and more! Schedule a demo!](https://www.cloudflare.com/plans/enterprise/contact/)
relatedBlades.leftLinkLoggedIn: [Enterprise plans include Turnstile, and more! Schedule a demo!](https://www.cloudflare.com/lp/turnstile/)

features.title: Better experiences
features.description: Give your web visitors an even better experience.  Turnstile confirms they are real with no visual puzzle - totally transparent to visitors.

features.title: Stronger privacy
features.description: Turnstile always preserves the privacy of web visitors on your site - without sacrificing effectiveness.  Unlike other CAPTCHA options, we never harvest data for ad retargeting.

features.title: Fast and free
features.description: Deploy in minutes with just a quick code snippet - and totally free of charge.

relatedBlades.title: 500 years on CAPTCHAs
relatedBlades.copy:
Humans spend about 500 years __each day__ solving CAPTCHAs - wasting time and creating frustration. 

This is why Cloudflare built a better alternative to CAPTCHAs with Managed Challenge and now Turnstile.

relatedBlades.title: Learn about Cloudflare, the global network built for the cloud.
Upgrade your security & performance with Turnstile for free!

planFeatures.name: Web Application Firewall (WAF)
planFeatures.description: Cloudflare Web Application Firewall's intuitive dashboard enables users to build powerful rules through easy clicks and also provides Terraform integration. Every request to the WAF is inspected against the rule engine and the threat intelligence curated from protecting millions of websites. Suspicious requests can be blocked, challenged or logged as per the needs of the user while legitimate requests are routed to the destination, agnostic of whether it lives on-premise or in the cloud.
